# ============================================
# üìù QUICK START GUIDE - TWO WALLET SYSTEM
# ============================================
#
# 1. Copy this file to .env.local
# 2. Generate 2 test wallets: node scripts/generate-wallets.js
#    - Admin Wallet: Handles deployment and server functions
#    - Relayer Wallet: Only pays gas for meta-transactions  
# 3. Get testnet funds from faucets for BOTH wallets:
#    - Mantle Sepolia: https://faucet.sepolia.mantle.xyz/
#    - Ethereum Sepolia: https://faucet.sepolia.dev/
# 4. Deploy contracts: npm run deploy:testnet (uses Admin wallet)
# 5. Update contract addresses above
# 6. Start development: npm run dev
#
# Two Wallet Benefits in Development:
# - Admin wallet: Secure, used only for important functions
# - Relayer wallet: Can be easily refilled with testnet funds
# - Simulates production security model
#
# Useful commands:
# - npm run dev (start frontend)
# - npm run server (start game server)
# - npm run relayer (start gasless relayer)
# - npm run deploy:testnet (deploy to testnet)
# - npm run verify:testnet (verify contracts)
